---
title: Calorie Smart Greek-Inspired Double Pork Chops with Lemony Roasted Potatoes and Feta Snap Peas
description: All the familiar flavours of Greek cuisine are packed into this better-for-you dinner! Garlicky pork, lemony roasted potatoes and feta snap peas round out this weeknight winner, which is finished with a dollop of yogurt sauce, to boot!

